(1, 's1-teknologi-informasi', 'S1 – Teknologi Informasi', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Teknologi Informasi.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>004</strong> : Ilmu Komputer / teknologi Informasi</li><li><strong>004.019</strong> : Prinsip Psikologis dalam Ilmu Komputer</li><li><strong>372.35</strong> : Sains &amp; teknologi untuk pendidikan dasar</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Teknologi Informasi, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/search?searchTerm=information+technology#/title\"><strong>Biodiversity Heritage Library</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://bookboon.com/en/search?q=information+technology\"><strong>Bookboon.com</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.free-ebooks.net/search/information+technology\"><strong>Free-ebooks.net</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.freetechbooks.com/\"><strong>Freetechbooks</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://archive.org/search.php?query=information%20technology&amp;sin=TXT\"><strong>Internet Archive</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.onlineprogrammingbooks.com/information-technology/\"><strong>OnlineProgrammingbooks.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.pdfdrive.net/information-technology-books.html\"><strong>Pdfdrive.net</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/weed%20technology/listing?q=information+technology&amp;searchWithinIds=96F2DAEB1066989CF72064E97B1D8112\"><strong>APSIPA Transactions on Signal and Information Processing : cambrige</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://journal.acs.org.au/index.php/ajis/issue/archive\"><strong>Australasian Journal of Information Systems</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://doaj.org/\"><strong>Directory Of Open Access Journals</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.is.cityu.edu.hk/staff/isrobert/ejisdc.htm\"><strong>Electronic Journal of Information Systems in Developing Countries</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://humanit.hb.se/issue/archive\"><strong>Human IT</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournals.bc.edu/ojs/index.php/ital/issue/archive\"><strong>Information Technology and Libraries</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mirlabs.org/ijcisim/archives.php\"><strong>International Journal of Computer Information Systems and Industrial Management Applications</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://http//airccse.org/journal/ijitcs/archives.html\"><strong>International journal Of Information Technology Convergence and Service ( IJITCS)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jbiomedsem.biomedcentral.com/articles?query=information+technology&amp;searchType=journalSearch&amp;tab=keyword\"><strong>Journal of Biomedical Semantics</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.hindawi.com/search/all/information+technology/\"><strong>Journal of Computer Networks and Communications : Hindawi</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jios.foi.hr/index.php/jios/issue/archive\"><strong>Journal of Information and Organizational Sciences</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.josis.org/index.php/josis/issue/archive\"><strong>Journal of Spatial Information Science</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mdpi.com/\"><strong>MDPI</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mecs-press.org/search.html?search=information%20technology\"><strong>Modern Education and Computer Science Press</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.sciencedirect.com/search?qs=information+technology&amp;authors=&amp;pub=&amp;volume=&amp;issue=&amp;page=&amp;origin=browse&amp;zone=qSearch\"><strong>Science Direct</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://id.portalgaruda.org/?ref=browse&amp;mod=viewjournal&amp;journal=7301&amp;issue=%20Vol%201,%20No%202%20(2014):%20Jurnal%20Teknologi%20Informasi%20dan%20Komunikasi%20dalam%20Pendidikan\"><strong>IPI</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://ejnteti.jteti.ugm.ac.id/index.php/JNTETI/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Nasional Teknik Elektro dan Teknologi Infromasi UGM</strong></a><strong> &nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://journal.uinjkt.ac.id/index.php/ti/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Teknik Informatika UINJKT</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://jurnal.unimed.ac.id/2012/index.php/teknologi/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Teknologi &amp; Informasi dalam Pendidikan UNIMED</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://teknosi.fti.unand.ac.id/index.php/teknosi/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Teknologi dan Sistem Informasi Universitas Andalas</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://jtsiskom.undip.ac.id/index.php/jtsiskom\"><strong>Jurnal Teknologi dan Sistem Komputer UNDIP</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://jtiik.ub.ac.id/index.php/jtiik/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Teknologi Informasi dan Ilmu Komputer</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.kemalapublisher.com/index.php/jmp/issue/view/36\"><strong>Jurnal Teknologi Informasi dan Komputer Kemala Indonesia</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://jurnal.unai.edu/index.php/teika/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Teknologi Informasi dan Komunikasi UNAI</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://juti.if.its.ac.id/index.php/juti/issue/archive\"><strong>JUTI : Jurnal Ilmiah Teknologi Informasi</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Encyclopedias</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.britannica.com/search?query=information%20technology\"><strong>Encyclopedia Britannica</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.encyclopedia.com/science-and-technology/computers-and-electrical-engineering/computers-and-computing/information-1\"><strong>Encyclopedia.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.newworldencyclopedia.org/p/index.php?title=Special%3ASearch&amp;profile=default&amp;search=information+technology&amp;fulltext=Search\"><strong>New World Encyclopedia</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.webopedia.com/sgsearch/results?cx=partner-pub-8768004398756183%3A6766915980&amp;cof=FORID%3A10&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;q=information+technology\"><strong>Webopedia&nbsp;</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information_technology\"><strong>Wikipedia</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Dictionaries</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"http://dictionary.cambridge.org/dictionary/english/information-technology\"><strong>Cambrige Dictionary</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/information-technology\"><strong>Collin Dictionary</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.consp.com/it-information-technology-terminology-dictionary\"><strong>Connet</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.techopedia.com/dictionary\"><strong>Techopedia</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.thefreedictionary.com/information+technology\"><strong>The Free Dictionary by Farlex</strong></a><strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.urbandictionary.com/define.php?term=information+technology\"><strong>Urban Dictionary</strong></a><strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.yourdictionary.com/information-technology#websters\"><strong>Your Dictionary</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Scholarships</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.bestvalueschools.com/information-technology-scholarships/\"><strong>Best Value Schools</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.collegescholarships.org/scholarships/it-students.htm\"><strong>College scolarships.org</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://internationalscholarships.ca/top-10-ict-scholarships-2017-2018-international-students/\"><strong>International Scholarships</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://online.king.edu/information-technology/9-scholarships-for-online-information-technology-students/\"><strong>King University Online</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.monash.edu/study/fees-scholarships/scholarships/find/international-student-scholarships-old/it-international-merit-5595ZB\"><strong>Monash University</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://polytechnic.purdue.edu/degrees/computer-and-information-technology/scholarships\"><strong>Purdue Polytechnic</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www1.rmit.edu.au/scholarships/it\"><strong>RMIT University</strong></a><strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.scholars4dev.com/category/field-of-study/information-technology-scholarships/\"><strong>Scholars4dev</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://scholarship-positions.com/information-technology-scholarships/2012/10/31/\"><strong>Scholarship-positions.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.scholarshipsandgrants.us/information-technology-scholarships/\"><strong>Scholarships and Grants</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.scholarships.com/financial-aid/college-scholarships/scholarships-by-type/technology-scholarships/\"><strong>Scholarships.com</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.eng.unimelb.edu.au/study/degrees/master-information-technology/fees-scholarships\"><strong>The University Of Melbourne</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Awards</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.aapa-ports.org/unifying/content.aspx?ItemNumber=21056\"><strong>AAPA American Association Of Port Authorities</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.bestvalueschools.com/lists/5-prestigious-information-technology-awards/\"><strong>Best Value Schools</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://gittawards.com.gh/\"><strong>GITTA G