(5, 's2-pendidikan-agama-islam', 'S2 – Pendidikan Agama Islam', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Pendidikan Agama Islam.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut:&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>2X7</strong> Filsafat dan Perkembangan Islam</li><li><strong>2X7.1</strong> Filsafat Islam&nbsp;</li><li><strong>2X7.15 </strong>Psikologi Islam</li><li><strong>2X7.3&nbsp;</strong>Pendidikan Islam, Sekolah Islam</li><li><strong>2X7.341 </strong>Pondok Pesantren</li><li><strong>371.077 </strong>Islamic Schools/Sekolah Islam</li><li><strong>372.84 </strong>Religion for Primary Education/Pelajaran Agama untuk Pendidikan Dasar<br>&nbsp;</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Pendidikan Agama Islam, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><p>1.&nbsp; Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Internasional, hampir semua jurnal berikut terindeks oleh Scopus:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://ajis.org/index.php/ajiss\"><strong>American Journal of Islam and Society</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://moraref.kemenag.go.id/archives/journal/98077985952795871\"><strong>IJISH</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.uinsi.ac.id/index.php/syamil/index\"><strong>SYAMIL</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.umy.ac.id/index.php/ijiep\"><strong>IJIEP</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://attarbiyah.iainsalatiga.ac.id/index.php/attarbiyah/\"><strong>ATTARBIYAH</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.uin-malang.ac.id/index.php/jpai\"><strong>J-PAI</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journal.umpo.ac.id/index.php/istawa/index\"><strong>Istawa</strong></a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;2.&nbsp;Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Nasional:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://journal.uhamka.ac.id/jpi\"><strong>Jurnal Pendidikan Islam</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.ejournal.staindirundeng.ac.id/index.php/tadib\"><strong>At-Ta\'dib</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.tarbiya.org/\"><strong>TARBIYA</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jurnaledukasia.org/index.php/edukasia\"><strong>Edukasia</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.neliti.com/journals/al-idarah\"><strong>Al-Idarah</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://books.google.com/\"><strong>BookGoogle.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://iou.edu.gm/\"><strong>Islamic Online University</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/\"><strong>ResearchGate</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.scribd.com/\"><strong>Scribd</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Encyclopedias</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://referenceworks.brill.com/display/package/eio\"><strong>Encyclopaedia of Islam (EI)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780195300826.001.0001/acref-9780195300826\"><strong>Oxford reference</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://muslimheritage.com/\"><strong>Muslim Heritage</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.britannica.com/\"><strong>Encyclopaedia Britannica</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Dictionaries</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://corpus.quran.com/\"><strong>Qur’anic Arabic Corpus</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://shamela.ws/\"><strong>Shamela Library</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.wordreference.com/\"><strong>WordReference Arabic-English Dictionary</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Scholarships</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.turkiyeburslari.gov.tr/\"><strong>Turkey Scholarships</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.chevening.org/\"><strong>Chevening Scholarship</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.