(7, 's1-hukum', 'S1 - Hukum', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Hukum.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>340</strong> : Ilmu Hukum</li><li><strong>340.1</strong> : Filsafat &amp; Teori Hukum</li><li><strong>340.5</strong> : Sistem Hukum</li><li><strong>340.9</strong> : Sejarah Hukum</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku bidang Hukum, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.freebookcentre.net/\"><strong>Free Book Centre Net&nbsp;</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://bookboon.com/en/marketing-and-law-ebooks\"><strong>BookBoon.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://e-booksdirectory.com/\"><strong>E-Books Directory</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.doabooks.org/\"><strong>Directory of Open Access book</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.oapen.org/search?expand=subject&amp;f1-subject=Law\"><strong>OAPEN</strong></a><a href=\"https://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/search/?query=english+literature\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://academic.oup.com/jla\"><strong>Journal of Legal Analysis, Oxford Academic</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://ojs.law.cornell.edu/index.php/joal\"><strong>Journal of Open Access to Law</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://dlj.law.duke.edu/about/submissions/open-access/\"><strong>Duke Law Journal</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.ccsenet.org/journal/index.php/jpl\"><strong>Journal of Politics and Law</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://academic.oup.com/ijlit\"><strong>International Journal of Law and Informatio