(9, 's1-tadris-matematika', 'S1 – Tadris Matematika', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Tadris Matematika.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>370</strong> : Pendidikan</li><li><strong>510</strong> : Matematika</li><li><strong>510.7</strong> : Pendidikan Matematika</li><li><strong>511</strong> : Prinsip Umum Matematika</li><li><strong>512</strong> : Aljabar</li><li><strong>513</strong> : Aritmatika</li><li><strong>515</strong> : Analisis, Kalkulus</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Tadris Matematika, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><p>1.&nbsp; Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Internasional, hampir semua jurnal berikut terindeks oleh Scopus:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.ams.org/journals/bull/all_issues.html\"><strong>American mathematical society</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.acadsci.fi/mathematica/\"><strong>Annales academia scientiarum fennica mathematica</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mdpi.com/2297-8747/22/1\"><strong>Mathematical and Computational Applications</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.hindawi.com/search/all/mathematics/\"><strong>Hindawi &nbsp;</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://journals.tubitak.gov.tr/math/lastIssue.htm\"><strong>Tubitak academic journal</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://http//www.math.armstrong.edu/faculty/budden/journals.html\"><strong>Mathematics journal with online open access</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.omicsonline.org/physical-mathematics.php\"><strong>Journal of physical mathematics</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://journals4free.com/?fq=class:mat&amp;fq=language:eng&amp;fq=spec:mathe\"><strong>Journal for free</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.sciencedirect.com/search?qs=mathematics&amp;pub=Advances%20in%20Mathematics&amp;show=25&amp;sortBy=relevance&amp;publicationTitles=272585&amp;accessTypes=openaccess&amp;lastSelectedFacet=accessTypes\"><strong>Science direct</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.epj.org/component/solr/?task=results#!q=mathematics&amp;sort=score%20desc&amp;rows=10&amp;f=language%3A%22en%22\"><strong>Epj.org</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://academic.oup.com/amrx/issue/2009/2\"><strong>Applied mathematics research express</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.springeropen.com/collections/rpdde-2014\"><strong>Springer open</strong></a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;2.&nbsp;Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Nasional:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://jurnal.unpad.ac.id/jmi/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Matematika Integratif</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://jms.fmipa.itb.ac.id/ojs_3.0.2/index.php/jms/issue/archive\"><strong>Jurnal Matematika dan Sains</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.jims-a.org/index.php/jimsa/issue/archive\"><strong>Journal of the Indonesian Mathematical Society</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://journals.itb.ac.id/index.php/jmfs/issue/archive\"><strong>Journal of Mathematical and Fundamental Sciences</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://bookboon.com/en/statistics-and-mathematics-ebooks\"><strong>BookBoon.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.oapen.org/search?keyword=mathematics;f1-language=English;f2-subject=Mathematics%20and%20science::Mathematics\"><strong>Oapen open access</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Encyclopedias</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Image_(mathematics)#Image_of_an_element\"><strong>Wikipedia</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780195300826.001