(15, 's1-akuntansi', 'S1 – Akuntansi', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Akuntansi.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>657</strong> : Akuntansi</li><li><strong>657.025</strong> : Direktori Akuntansi</li><li><strong>657.03 </strong>: Kamus Akuntansi</li><li><strong>657.42</strong> : Akuntansi Biaya</li><li><strong>657.452</strong> : Laporan Audit</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Akuntansi, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.oapen.org/search?keyword=accounting\"><strong>Oapen Open Access</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.doabooks.org/doab?func=search&amp;uiLanguage=en&amp;template=&amp;query=accounting\"><strong>Directory of Open Access books</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.intechopen.com/search?q=accounting\"><strong>Intech Open Science</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://bookboon.com/en/search?q=accounting\"><strong>Bookboon.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.freebookcentre.net/Business/Accounting-Books.html\"><strong>Freebookcentre.net</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.pdfdrive.net/accounting-e20155724.html\"><strong>Pdfdrive.net</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.tandfebooks.com/action/doSearch?access=user&amp;AllField=accounting&amp;ConceptID=9392&amp;startPage=&amp;ConceptID=10752\"><strong>Taylor &amp; Francis Ebooks</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.redalyc.org/BusquedaArticuloRevista.oa\"><strong>Revista de Contabilidad</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://web.usm.my/aamj/articles.html\"><strong>Asian Acade