(16, 's1-psikologi', 'S1 - Psikologi', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Psikologi.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>100</strong> : Filsafat &amp; Psikologi</li><li><strong>150</strong> : Psikologi</li><li><strong>150.1</strong> : Filsafat dan teori Psikologi</li><li><strong>150.19</strong> : Sistem Psikologi, Pandangan Psikologi</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Psikologi, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.e-booksdirectory.com/\"><strong>E-Books Directory</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.doabooks.org/doab?func=search&amp;uiLanguage=en&amp;template=&amp;query=psychology\"><strong>Directory of Open Access Books (DOAB)</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.bookrix.com/books.html\"><strong>BookRix</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.free-ebooks.net/category/psychology\"><strong>Free-Ebooks.net</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.intechopen.com/search?q=psychology\"><strong>INTECH Open Access Books</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.ebooks-free-net.net/ebooks-free-Psychology.asp\"><strong>Ebooks Free Net</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://manybooks.net/categories/PSY\"><strong>ManyBooks</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.all-about-psychology.com/\"><strong>The All About Psychology Website</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><p>1.&nbsp; Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Internasional, hampir semua jurnal berikut terindeks oleh Scopus:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http