ul I\'anah, S.ST., M.Kes. </strong><a href=\"https://sinta.kemdikbud.go.id/authors/profile/6710973\">(</a><a href=\"https://sinta.kemdikbud.go.id/authors/profile/6765826\">Sinta ID : 6765826</a><a href=\"https://sinta.kemdikbud.go.id/authors/profile/6710973\">)</a>, <a href=\"https://scholar.google.co.id/citations?hl=en&amp;user=YN9ZxEEAAAAJ\">(</a><a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?hl=id&amp;user=Uj_cCnQAAAAJ\">GS ID: Uj_cCnQAAAAJ</a><a href=\"https://scholar.google.co.id/citations?hl=en&amp;user=YN9ZxEEAAAAJ\">)</a></li></ul>', '2024-12-18 06:59:16', '2025-05-08 09:02:32'),
(18, 's1-sistem-informasi', 'S1 – Sistem Informasi', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Sistem Informasi.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>000</strong> : Karya Umum</li><li><strong>004 - 006</strong> : Teknologi Informasi &amp; Komputer</li><li><p><strong>005.7</strong> : Sistem Informasi</p><p>&nbsp;</p></li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Sistem Informasi, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"http://bookboon.com/en/it-programming-ebooks-zip\"><strong>Bookboon.com</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.ebook3000.com/\"><strong>E-Book3000</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.tradepub.com/\"><strong>TradePub</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mdpi.com/books/pdfview/book/117\"><strong>MDPI Books</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"http://www.freebookcentre.net/CompuScience/Free-Computer-Graphics-Books-Download.html\"><strong>Frebookcenter.net</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.e-booksdirectory.com/details.php?ebook=11461\"><strong>Ebook Directory</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.pdfdrive.net/computer-science-books.html\"><strong>PDFDRIVE</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><p>1.&nbsp; Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Internasional, hampir semua jurnal berikut terindeks oleh Scopus:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.amcs.uz.zgora.pl/?action=paper&amp;paper=1340\"><strong>AMCS</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.info.uaic.ro/bin/Annals/XXVI1\"><strong>Faculty of computer science</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.cit.iit.bas.bg/CIT_2017/CIT_17-2.html\"><strong>IICT</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://cit.fer.hr/index.php/CIT/index\"><strong>CIT</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://jcsitnet.com/vol-5-no-1-june-2017-current-issue-jcsit\"><strong>JCSIT</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.aece.ro/abstractplus.php?year=2015&amp;number=3&amp;article=18\"><strong>AACE</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://doaj.org/\"><strong>DOAJ</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/319186776_Vacancy_Induced_Energy_Band_Gap_Changes_of_Semiconducting_Zigzag_Single_Walled_Carbon_Nanotubes\"><strong>ResearchGate</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.mii.lt/informatics_in_education/htm/infedu.2017.01.htm\"><strong>Informatic for Education</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://jios.foi.hr/index.php/jios/index\"><strong>FOI</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.infona.pl/resource/bwmeta1.element.baztech-journal-0239-7228-bulletin_of_the_polish_academy_of_sciences__technical_sciences/tab/jContent?q=sc*op*l_0*c_0journalYear_0FACET%3Aeq%3A90fd8137-a46e-4353-8a90-b620f268cdc9._002017*p_0cP.1&amp;localeQueryString=field%3D%5EjournalYear%26value%3D%5E_02017%26resourceId%3Dbwmeta1.element.baztech-554ca3e1-af20-4298-b4f0-af1d5389b266%26tabType%3Dsummary%26availability%3DNOT_AVAILABLE%26supportedAjaxTabs%3Dreferences%26supportedAjaxTabs%3Dcontributors%26supportedAjaxTabs%3DjContent\"><strong>Portal Komunikacii Naukoweii</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://hrcak.srce.hr/god-titius\"><strong>HR Cak</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://etasr.com/index.php/ETASR/index\"><strong>ETASR</strong></a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;2.&nbsp;Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Nasional:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://ejournal.unisnu.ac.id/index/index\"><strong>UIN Ulama Jepara</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://ejournal.narotama.ac.id/index.php/cari\"><strong>Universitas Narotama</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://jutisi.maranatha.edu/index.php/jutisi/index\"><strong>Universitas Kristen Duta Wacana</strong></a