rong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.iup.edu/compsci/undergrad/students/student-awards/\"><strong>Indiana University Of Pensilvania</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://computerscience.tcnj.edu/students/accomplishments-of-recent-students/awards/\"><strong>TCNJ</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://designday.msu.edu/computer-science/awards\"><strong>Michigan State University</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Dosen</strong></i></h4><ul><li><strong>Saifullah, M.Kom. (Sinta ID : 6780797), (GS ID: I8J7aQsAAAAJ)</strong></li><li><strong>Fajriyanto, M.Kom. (Sinta ID : 6906060), (GS ID: 9lBTl6EAAAAJ)</strong></li><li><strong>Nur Azise, M.Kom. (Sinta ID : 6906680), (GS ID: CjW6m1oAAAAJ)</strong></li><li><strong>Zaehol Fatah, M.Kom. (Sinta ID : 6850583), (GS ID: 90pVThcAAAAJ)</strong></li><li><strong>Achmad Bajuri, M.Kom. (Sinta ID : 6714604) (GS ID: 3qvgiz4AAAAJ)</strong></li><li><strong>Ahmad Lutfi, M.Kom. (Sinta ID : 6714593), (GS ID: 4PaiKgIAAAAJ)</strong></li><li><strong>Muhammad Ali RIdla, M.Kom. (Sinta ID : 6826489), (GS ID: 45LHtJYAAAAJ)</strong></li></ul>', '2024-12-18 07:00:05', '2025-12-06 15:01:05'),
(19, 'd3-budidaya-perikanan', 'D3 – Budidaya Perikanan', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Budidaya Perikanan.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;600</strong> : Teknologi</p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;630</strong> : Perikanan, Peternakan, Agrikultur, Pertanian dan subjek terkait</p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;639.31</strong> : Peternakan Ikan Air Tawar, Budidaya Ikan Air Tawar</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; - &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>639.32 : </strong>Peternakan Ikan di Air Asin dan Air Payau</p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;639.34</strong> : Peternakan Ikan di Akuarium, Budidaya Ikan Hias</p><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Budidaya Perikanan, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Perpustakaan:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>Catalog</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><p>1.&nbsp; Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Internasional, hampir semua jurnal berikut terindeks oleh Scopus:</p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/journal/are\"><strong>Aquaculture</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/journal/17497345\"><strong>Journal of the World Aquaculture Society (JWAS)</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/journal/anu\"><strong>Aquaculture Nutrition</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/fish-and-shellfish-immunology\"><strong>Fish &amp; Shellfish Immunology</strong></a></p><p>&nbsp;2.&nbsp;Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Nasional:</p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://journal.ipb.ac.id/index.php/jai/index\"><strong>Jurnal Akuakultur Indonesia</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://journal.ipb.ac.id/index.php/jurnalikt\"><strong>Jurnal Ilmu dan Teknologi Kelautan Tropis</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://ejournalfpikunipa.ac.id/index.php/JSAI/\"><strong>Jurnal Sumberdaya Akuatik Indoensia (JSAI)</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://sinta.kemdikbud.go.id/journals/profile/2761\"><strong>Jurnal Penyuluhan Perikanan dan Kelautan</strong></a></p><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://perpustakaan.kkp.go.id/knowledgerepository/\"><strong>Panduan Budidaya Ikan Air Tawar</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://redasamudera.id/balai-riset-perikanan-budidaya-air-tawar-dan-penyuluhan-perikanan/\"><strong>Akuakultur Berkelanjutan di Indonesia</strong></a></p><h4><i><strong>Encyclopedias</strong></i></h4><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.wiley.com/en-sg\"><strong>Wiley</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/\"><strong>ScienceDirect</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.fao.org/fisheries/en\"><strong>FAO Fisheries</strong></a></p><h4><i><strong>Dictionaries</strong></i></h4><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.aquadocs.org/\"><strong>AquaDocs Glossary&nbsp;</strong></a><strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.noaa.gov/\"><strong>NOAA Glossary</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.routledge.com/\"><strong>CRC Press</strong></a></p><h4><i><strong>Scholarships</strong></i></h4><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://lpdp.kemenkeu.go.id/\"><strong>Beasiswa LPDP (Lembaga Pengelola Dana Pendidikan)</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://kkp.go.id/news/news-detail/kkp-buka-pendaftaran-tarunai-baru-2024-ada-jalur-umum-khusus.html\"><strong>Beasiswa Unggulan Kementerian Kelautan dan Perikanan (KKP)</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://beasiswa.undip.ac.id/\"><strong>Beasiswa Universitas Diponegoro (UNDIP)</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://australiaawards.com.au/\"><strong>Australia Awards Scholarships (AAS)</strong></a></p><h4><i><strong>Awards</strong></i></h4><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://kalpataru.menlhk.go.id/\"><strong>Kalpataru Award</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.ipb.ac.id/\"><strong>Indonesia Fisheries Award</strong></a></p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.fao.org/fishery/en\"><strong>FAO World Fisheries Award</strong></a></p>', '2024-12-18 07:00:16', '2026-02-12 13:59:06');
