(21, 's1-hukum-ekonomi-syariah', 'S1 – Hukum Ekonomi Syariah', '<h4><i><strong>Buku/Books</strong></i></h4><p>Perpustakaan memiliki banyak koleksi buku dan bahan bacaan lainnya dalam bidang Hukum Ekonomi Syariah.<br>Buku-buku di klasifikasikan menurut nomor klasifikasi (DDC) sebagai berikut :&nbsp;</p><ul><li>2X3 – Fiqh Muamalah</li><li>2X4 – Hukum Ekonomi Syariah</li><li>297.1 – Al-Qur\'an</li><li>297.2 – Hadis</li><li>297.14 – Fiqh</li><li>330 : Ilmu Ekonomi</li><li>340 : Ilmu Hukum Umum</li><li>346.08 : Hukum Ekonomi</li><li>346.167 : Hukum Perbankan dan Keuangan Syariah</li></ul><p>&nbsp;Untuk mengetahui buku Ekonomi Syariah, penelusuran dapat dilakukan melalui Katalog Online Perpustakaan (<a href=\"https://opac.lib.ibrahimy.ac.id/\"><strong>SLIMS/OPAC</strong></a>)<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><h4><i><strong>E-Journals</strong></i></h4><p>1.&nbsp; Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Internasional, hampir semua jurnal berikut terindeks oleh Scopus:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.emeraldgrouppublishing.com/journal/jiabr\"><strong>Journal of Islamic Accounting and Business Research (JIABR)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.emeraldgrouppublishing.com/journal/ies\"><strong>Islamic Economic Studies (IES)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.emeraldgrouppublishing.com/journal/imefm\"><strong>International Journal of Islamic and Middle Eastern Finance and Management (IMEFM)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.ibtra.com/\"><strong>Journal of Islamic Economics, Banking and Finance (JIEBF)</strong></a></li><li><strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://iijif.com/journal-evaluation/\"><strong>ISRA International Journal of Islamic Finance (IIJIF)</strong></a></li><li><strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://ajis.org/index.php/ajiss\"><strong>American Journal of Islamic Social Sciences (AJISS)</strong></a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;2.&nbsp;Akses Terbuka (Open Access) Jurnal Nasional:</p><ul><li><strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://e-journal.iain-palangkaraya.ac.id/index.php/maslahah\"><strong>UAl-Mashlahah</strong></a></li><li><strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://journal.unismuh.ac.id/index.php/jhes\"><strong>Jurnal Hukum Ekonomi Syariah (JHES)</strong></a></li><li><strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://journal.uinjkt.ac.id/index.php/jhi\"><strong>Jurnal Hukum Islam (JHI)</strong></a></li><li><strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://journal.uinjkt.ac.id/index.php/iqtishad\"><strong>Jurnal Al-Iqtishad</strong></a></li><li><strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://justiciaislamica.iainponorogo.ac.id\"><strong>Justicia Islamica</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>E-Books</strong></i></h4><p>Database&nbsp;E-Book&nbsp;yang dapat diakses secara terbuka (Open Access) sbb:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.doabooks.org/\"><strong>DOAB (Directory of Open Access Books)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://irti.org/\"><strong>IRTI (Islamic Research and Training Institute)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/\"><strong>ResearchGate</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://link.springer.com/\"><strong>Springer</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Encyclopedias</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.oxfordreference.com/\"><strong>The Oxford Encyclopedia of Islam and Law</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://brill.com/\"><strong>Encyclopedia of Islam</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/374371563_The_Palgrave_Encyclopedia_of_Islamic_Economics_and_Finance\"><strong>Encyclopedia of Islamic Finance</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://link.springer.com/\"><strong>The Palgrave Handbook of Islamic Finance</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.routledge.com/\"><strong>Routledge Handbook of Islamic Law</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Dictionaries</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.oxfordreference.com/\"><strong>Oxford Dictionary &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></a><strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.vocabulary.com/dictionary/management\"><strong>Vocabbulary&nbsp;</strong></a><strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.al-mawrid.org/\"><strong>Al-Mawrid&nbsp;</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"http://dictionary.cambridge.org/dictionary/english/management?q=Management\"><strong>Cambridge Dictionary</strong></a><strong> &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></li><li><a href=\"https://www.najaf.org/english/glossary\"><strong>Online Fiqh Glossary</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Scholarships</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.iium.edu.my/v2/\"><strong>International Islamic University Malaysia (IIUM)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.sharjah.ac.ae/\"><strong>University of Sharjah (UAE)&nbsp;</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.uii.ac.id/\"><strong>Universitas Islam Indonesia (UII)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.dfat.gov.au/people-to-people/australia-awards\"><strong>Australia Awards</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://lpdp.kemenkeu.go.id/en/\"><strong>Beasiswa LPDP</strong></a></li></ul><h4><i><strong>Awards</strong></i></h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.gifa.org/\"><strong>The Global Islamic Finance Award (GIFA)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://kingfaisalprize.org/\"><strong>The King Faisal International Prize for Islamic Studies</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.isdb.org/\"><strong>The Islamic Development Bank (IsDB)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.oic-oci.org/\"><strong>OIC (Organization of Islamic Cooperation)</strong></a></li><li><a href=\"https://icesco.org/en/\"><strong>ISESCO Prize for Islamic Studies</strong></a></li></ul>', '2025-01-06 05:13:36', '2025-12-07 07:40:29'),
